title: Sharp One Bedroom -Near Lake of Isles - 2211 Colfax
posting_body: ['LARGE 600 SQ FT 1 BEDROOM WITH FREE PARKING-', 'This is a sharp building with a wonderful large carpeted one bedroom available in Uptown.', 'It is a great space!', 'In a great location!', 'with restaurants, parks, lakes, museums, and downtown all within minutes of home.', ' There is built in AC to keep you cool on those hot summer nights and we pay the heat so you will be cozy throughout the winter.', 'You will never have to wait with several laundry machines on-site.', 'Appliances are newer and full size, so you can cook to your hearts delight!', 'And did we say you will get a free parking space too!', 'Text Darlene', 'show contact info', 'for showing today!', '-free parking', '-on site laundry', '-fiber optic internet available', '-super maintenance', '-cats ok with additional pet rent ($20) and deposit ($200)', '-bus line 1 half block away', 'IF YOU LIKE A VIDEO TOUR OF THIS APARTMENT', 'JUST EMAIL', 'A REQUEST AND WE WILL SEND YOU A LINK', 'Professionally managed by the Hornig Companies.', '<URL>.']
